---
description: "High-risk areas policy"
alwaysApply: true
---

High-risk change policy (fail closed):
- auth/permissions/crypto/payments: must be flagged in {artifact root}/risk.md
- deps changes: require {artifact root}/dependency-review.md
- docker/ci changes: require {artifact root}/infra-review.md
- db migrations: require {artifact root}/db-review.md with reversibility and rollback notes

If uncertain about risk impact, mark the task BLOCKED and explain precisely what info is missing.
